oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bank of McLemoresville pre-remodel
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Interior view of the Bank of McLemoresville prior to remodeling. Josiah Conrad "Connie" McKinney (1877-1955) and Zettie Gardner (1887-1980) are standing behind the counter to the right. Ocie J Presley (1931-1974) is standing next to them, and another man is seated behind the counter on the far left..
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Banks
